## ğŸŸ¢ STEP 3: Data Types (Language Alphabet)

JavaScript talks in types.

### Primitive Types

* Number
* String
* Boolean
* Undefined
* Null
* Symbol (later)
* BigInt (later)

### Non-Primitive

* Object
* Array
* Function

```js
