## ğŸŸ¢ STEP 4: Operators (How JS Thinks)

Operators are **actions on data**.

### Must learn

* Arithmetic: `+ - * / %`
* Assignment: `= += -=`
* Comparison: `== === != !==`
* Logical: `&& || !`

ğŸ”¥ Important:

* `==` vs `===` (this will haunt you later if ignored)

